<lg n="1">
    <ln n="1"><char ref="#Belle">Belle:</char> When I get to know him</ln>
    <ln n="2">We'll find more things to say</ln>
    <ln n="3">One day I will reach him</ln>
    <ln n="4">There has to be a way</ln>
</lg>

<lg n="2">
    <ln n="5">Everyone needs someone</ln>
    <ln n="6">He must need someone, too</ln>
    <ln n="7">When I get to know him better</ln>
    <ln n="8">Here's what I will do</ln>
</lg>

<lg n="3">
    <ln n="9">I'll read him stories</ln>
