    <ln n="11">All filled with wonder</ln>
    <ln n="12">Magic worlds where</ln>
    <ln n="13">The impossible</ln>
    <ln n="14">Becomes the everyday</ln>
</lg>

<lg n="4">
    <ln n="15">We'll find a mountaintop</ln>
